		<title>Organizational Consultation</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="/34-services/consultation/407-organizational-consultation"/>
		<published>2009-07-20T15:54:33+00:00</published>
		<updated>2009-07-20T15:54:33+00:00</updated>
		<id>/34-services/consultation/407-organizational-consultation</id>
		<author>
			<name>Avtar Gill</name>
			<email>agill@ocadu.ca</email>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;h3&gt;Organizational Accessibility Consultation Services&lt;/h3&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Beyond the accessibility of its infrastructure, corporations must be aware of new guidelines and standards for the inclusiveness of Customer Service policies and ICT based technologies. Having worked directly with the standards bodies, the ATRC is developing supportive training resources and materials to support the implementation of these new standards.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://standards.iso.org/ittf/PubliclyAvailableStandards/index.html&quot;&gt;ISO standards &lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;h3&gt;Organizational Accessibility Consultation Services&lt;/h3&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Beyond the accessibility of its infrastructure, corporations must be aware of new guidelines and standards for the inclusiveness of Customer Service policies and ICT based technologies. Having worked directly with the standards bodies, the ATRC is developing supportive training resources and materials to support the implementation of these new standards.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://standards.iso.org/ittf/PubliclyAvailableStandards/index.html&quot;&gt;ISO standards &lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</content>
