	<entry>
		<title>Web and Information Technology Accessibility/Consultation Services</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="/34-services/consultation/396-web-and-information-technology-accessibilityconsultation-services"/>
		<published>2009-02-17T16:41:00+00:00</published>
		<updated>2009-02-17T16:41:00+00:00</updated>
		<id>/34-services/consultation/396-web-and-information-technology-accessibilityconsultation-services</id>
		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;In addition to working directly with individuals of all abilities, the ATRC works with international organizations that create standards for accessible information design, including the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.mcss.gov.on.ca/mcss/english/pillars/accessibilityOntario&quot;&gt;AODA&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.w3.org/WAI/&quot;&gt;W3C&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.imsglobal.org/accessibility/index.html&quot;&gt;IMS Global Learning Consortium&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To support organizations that want to insure that their websites and technologies are meeting the widest possible audience we have a growing number of services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://websavvy.idrc.ocad.ca/&quot;&gt;Web-Savvy&lt;/a&gt; (Website accessibility evaluation service)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/index.php?option=com_content&amp;amp;task=view&amp;amp;id=325&amp;amp;Itemid=133&quot;&gt;Video Access Media Centre&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;p&gt;In addition to working directly with individuals of all abilities, the ATRC works with international organizations that create standards for accessible information design, including the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.mcss.gov.on.ca/mcss/english/pillars/accessibilityOntario&quot;&gt;AODA&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.w3.org/WAI/&quot;&gt;W3C&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.imsglobal.org/accessibility/index.html&quot;&gt;IMS Global Learning Consortium&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To support organizations that want to insure that their websites and technologies are meeting the widest possible audience we have a growing number of services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://websavvy.idrc.ocad.ca/&quot;&gt;Web-Savvy&lt;/a&gt; (Website accessibility evaluation service)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/index.php?option=com_content&amp;amp;task=view&amp;amp;id=325&amp;amp;Itemid=133&quot;&gt;Video Access Media Centre&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
